    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors against project requirements for MRL 5. Seven factors were assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels. Six factors were not assessed due to epistemic gaps identified during the assessment. Despite the structural completeness of this package under the Minimal profile, the absence of the structured bindsRequirement binding means traceability to the formal project requirements document is carried only in narrative prose. The overall credibility posture does not meet the thresholds needed for a positive submission decision; however, this record is accepted as a complete Minimal-profile UnitOfAssurance for archival and review purposes.",
